					<SUBPROJECT text="Counting and displaying RPM" href="rpm-counting.html"/>
					<SUBPROJECT text="Storing engine information in the cloud" href="wifi.html"/>
					<SUBPROJECT text="Design and printing of a case" href="case-design.html"/>
				</ul>
				<p>Each sub-project will have a page where the progress will be logged in chronological order.</p>
